goals.question: What is the correlation between the closing price and volume traded?

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['date'])
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='open', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the trend of the opening price over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Close'] = pd.to_numeric(data['Close'], errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='Close', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['Close'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of the closing price?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data['volume'] = pd.to_numeric(data['volume'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.groupby('date')['volume'].mean().reset_index()
    ax = sns.barplot(x='date', y='volume', data=data)
    ax.axhline(y=data['volume'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Average Volume')
    ax.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
